The second level concerns a human re-reading of OCR work and scanned documents in order to check the whole text. After proofreading, we obtain a 1/5000 reliability rate. This rate is also a function of the quality of the digitization performed.
OCR becomes more and more interesting because the technological evolutions should make it possible to integrate in the work of OCRisation, a markup work.
